# Common Mistakes

## Forgetting Package Statement

Wrong:

```java
public class Student {

}
```

inside package folder.

---

Correct:

```java
package student;

public class Student {

}
```

---

## Wrong Folder Structure

Package:

```java
package student;
```

File must be inside:

```text
student/
```

folder.

